679
00:26:05,400 --> 00:26:06,090
just tell me.

680
00:26:06,090 --> 00:26:06,890
I can do it all.

681
00:26:07,330 --> 00:26:08,790
There's not much to help with.

682
00:26:08,790 --> 00:26:10,270
Just the usual chores.

683
00:26:10,380 --> 00:26:11,740
I can handle it myself.

684
00:26:14,220 --> 00:26:15,550
But coming early is fine.

685
00:26:15,550 --> 00:26:17,250
You can join us

686
00:26:17,980 --> 00:26:18,580
