697
00:26:42,350 --> 00:26:44,330
She wants to make a few outfits for you.

698
00:26:44,330 --> 00:26:46,250
Tell your mom not to go to any trouble.

699
00:26:46,250 --> 00:26:47,980
I just wear whatever,

700
00:26:48,240 --> 00:26:49,700
