706
00:27:08,180 --> 00:27:08,770
I write it down

707
00:27:08,770 --> 00:27:10,030
and have my mom make it.

708
00:27:11,700 --> 00:27:12,300
I actually

709
00:27:13,090 --> 00:27:13,700
brought something

710
00:27:13,700 --> 00:27:14,550
