719
00:27:42,030 --> 00:27:43,090
This...

720
00:27:44,740 --> 00:27:47,200
This is so beautiful.

721
00:27:47,440 --> 00:27:48,900
Your mom is incredible.

722
00:27:49,050 --> 00:27:50,250
There's a skirt, too.

723
00:27:50,440 --> 00:27:51,400
If it doesn't fit,

724
00:27:51,400 --> 00:27:52,750
I'll take it back and alter it.

725
00:27:52,750 --> 00:27:53,950
It's a two-piece set?

726
00:27:55,720 --> 00:27:56,180
This...

727
00:27:56,510 --> 00:27:57,090
It's so colorful.

728
00:27:57,090 --> 00:27:58,350
