729
00:27:58,420 --> 00:27:59,610
Not at all.

730
00:27:59,750 --> 00:28:00,510
It suits you perfectly.

731
00:28:00,510 --> 00:28:01,240
It suits your elegance.

732
00:28:01,240 --> 00:28:02,090
It's very classy.

733
00:28:02,090 --> 00:28:02,980
Really?

734
00:28:03,590 --> 00:28:04,290
Do I...

735
00:28:05,050 --> 00:28:05,570
Does it

736
00:28:05,680 --> 00:28:06,480
