751
00:28:34,000 --> 00:28:35,060
You're so skilled.

752
00:28:35,240 --> 00:28:36,350
I'm glad you like it.

753
00:28:36,350 --> 00:28:37,270
I love it.

754
00:28:39,270 --> 00:28:39,670
Who...

755
00:28:40,550 --> 00:28:41,380
Who is this?

756
00:28:41,640 --> 00:28:42,640
It's Mrs. Zheng.

757
00:28:43,500 --> 00:28:43,920
No.

758
00:28:44,460 --> 00:28:45,550
It's a superstar.

759
00:28:46,050 --> 00:28:46,780
A superstar!

760
00:28:46,940 --> 00:28:48,030
You're never serious.

761
00:28:48,030 --> 00:28:48,960
It looks so good.

762
00:28:49,160 --> 00:28:51,020
Are these new clothes you bought?

763
00:28:51,550 --> 00:28:53,140
Zhuang Zhuang's mother made this for me.

764
00:28:53,140 --> 00:28:54,940
Zhuang Zhuang's mother made it?

765
00:28:55,050 --> 00:28:55,720
Zhuang Zhuang,

766
00:28:55,720 --> 00:28:57,200
ask your mother to make one for me too.

767
00:28:57,200 --> 00:28:57,660
Sure.

768
00:28:57,750 --> 00:28:58,690
So that I can

769
00:28:58,830 --> 00:29:00,490
