773
00:29:09,960 --> 00:29:11,240
So beautiful.

774
00:29:11,480 --> 00:29:12,900
Don't I look good usually?

775
00:29:12,900 --> 00:29:14,410
You always look great.

776
00:29:14,500 --> 00:29:16,700
But today you are especially stunning.

777
00:29:19,130 --> 00:29:20,550
[Beijing Station]

778
00:29:20,630 --> 00:29:21,700
[Tickets]

779
00:29:23,250 --> 00:29:23,880
Hello.

780
00:29:24,010 --> 00:29:25,330
One ticket to Guangzhou, please.

781
00:29:25,330 --> 00:29:26,120
223 yuan.

782
00:29:27,180 --> 00:29:30,450
[Ticket Hall]

783
00:29:27,500 --> 00:29:27,850
Hello.

784
00:29:27,850 --> 00:29:29,380
I want a ticket to Nanchang.

785
00:29:29,680 --> 00:29:30,530
Nanchang.

786
00:29:32,750 --> 00:29:33,200
Hello.

787
00:29:33,440 --> 00:29:33,770
Hello.

788
00:29:33,770 --> 00:29:35,270
Ten seated tickets for Train 134

789
00:29:35,270 --> 00:29:36,730
