792
00:29:39,460 --> 00:29:40,500
They asked me to buy tickets.

793
00:29:40,500 --> 00:29:41,360
Which company?

794
00:29:41,500 --> 00:29:42,560
Wait a moment.

795
00:29:46,480 --> 00:29:48,340
Here's the introduction letter.

796
00:29:56,680 --> 00:29:57,530
1,170 yuan.

797
00:29:58,140 --> 00:29:58,470
Okay.

798
00:30:02,930 --> 00:30:05,680
[Ticket Hall]

799
00:30:14,460 --> 00:30:15,220
-Ten tickets.
-Thank you.

800
00:30:15,220 --> 00:30:16,150
You're welcome.

801
00:30:17,460 --> 00:30:20,080
[Ticket Office]

802
00:30:20,240 --> 00:30:20,900
Kid.

803
00:30:21,400 --> 00:30:22,110
Where's the money

804
00:30:22,110 --> 00:30:22,880
I told you to bring last week?

805
00:30:22,880 --> 00:30:24,940
-Collecting rangehoods!
-Where’s the money?

806
00:30:24,940 --> 00:30:25,980
Is it in your pocket?

807
00:30:25,980 --> 00:30:27,200
Where did you put the money?

808
00:30:27,200 --> 00:30:28,200
Not in the pocket.

809
00:30:28,610 --> 00:30:29,480
Don't meddle.

810
00:30:32,920 --> 00:30:33,980
Where's the money?

811
00:30:34,180 --> 00:30:35,240
The money you made.

812
00:30:35,700 --> 00:30:36,100
Money.

813
00:30:36,960 --> 00:30:38,420
Why are you bullying a disabled person?

814
00:30:38,420 --> 00:30:39,790
Are you two even human?

815
00:30:39,920 --> 00:30:41,180
None of your business.

816
00:30:43,140 --> 00:30:44,330
I'll kill you!

817
00:30:44,380 --> 00:30:45,400
He's crazy. Run.

818
00:30:45,480 --> 00:30:46,090
He's crazy.

819
00:30:46,090 --> 00:30:47,500
I'll kill you!

820
00:30:47,680 --> 00:30:48,030
I...

821
00:30:58,380 --> 00:30:59,380
Are you okay, kid?

822
00:31:02,000 --> 00:31:02,600
Come here.

823
00:31:08,000 --> 00:31:09,000
Are you all right?

824
00:31:10,610 --> 00:31:12,500
Where do you live?

825
00:31:15,720 --> 00:31:17,400
I can hear you.

826
00:31:17,640 --> 00:31:19,010
You can hear a little?

827
00:31:24,420 --> 00:31:26,030
What is this?

828
00:31:28,200 --> 00:31:29,090
A hearing aid?

829
00:31:30,030 --> 00:31:31,880
Artificial cochlear.

830
00:31:33,830 --> 00:31:34,850
Artificial what?

831
00:31:46,830 --> 00:31:49,390
[Artificial cochlear]

832
00:31:47,140 --> 00:31:49,510
Cochlear.

833
00:31:50,420 --> 00:31:51,830
Artificial cochlear?

834
00:31:55,830 --> 00:31:57,790
[Artificial cochlear. Put it in]

835
00:31:59,760 --> 00:32:01,660
[And I can hear.]

836
00:32:03,270 --> 00:32:03,980
Really?

837
00:32:05,460 --> 00:32:06,140
How did you

838
00:32:06,680 --> 00:32:07,460
go deaf?

839
00:32:10,840 --> 00:32:12,920
[I had a fever when I was young]

840
00:32:14,730 --> 00:32:16,250
[I had a fever when I was young
and then I went deaf.]

841
00:32:18,110 --> 00:32:20,340
[I couldn't talk after that.]

842
00:32:21,140 --> 00:32:23,290
You go deaf first, then mute, too?

843
00:32:24,980 --> 00:32:27,200
Where did you get this done?

844
00:32:29,830 --> 00:32:31,550
[In Beijing.]

845
00:32:33,610 --> 00:32:34,200
Child,

846
00:32:34,960 --> 00:32:37,170
write down everything you know

847
00:32:37,440 --> 00:32:39,090
