848
00:32:39,220 --> 00:32:41,450
Which hospital? Which specialist?

849
00:32:48,910 --> 00:32:49,550
[Beijing Association Hospital
ENT Department]

850
00:32:49,580 --> 00:32:50,610
[Attending Physician Zhang Jicong]

851
00:32:52,140 --> 00:32:52,660
Child,

852
00:32:53,330 --> 00:32:55,440
