873
00:34:25,760 --> 00:34:27,020
Thank you, Mrs. Zheng.

874
00:34:27,880 --> 00:34:28,280
Here.

875
00:34:28,820 --> 00:34:29,820
Have a tangerine.

876
00:34:32,550 --> 00:34:33,409
Zhuang Zhuang,

877
00:34:33,960 --> 00:34:34,710
why have you booked

878
00:34:34,710 --> 00:34:36,110
