882
00:34:41,550 --> 00:34:42,750
yet you pull this on us

883
00:34:42,780 --> 00:34:44,440
and just stop coming to class.

884
00:34:45,510 --> 00:34:46,360
Zhuang Zhuang,

885
00:34:46,360 --> 00:34:48,090
I think you looking for odd jobs

886
00:34:48,280 --> 00:34:49,570
everywhere in Beijing

887
00:34:49,860 --> 00:34:51,070
isn't a long-term solution.

888
00:34:51,070 --> 00:34:52,270
It's not safe either.

889
00:34:55,489 --> 00:34:58,460
[Yue Ru]

890
00:34:56,460 --> 00:34:58,150
This is a designer that a friend of mine

891
00:34:58,150 --> 00:34:59,570
worked with before.

892
00:34:59,820 --> 00:35:01,430
He said this designer

893
00:35:01,350 --> 00:35:01,930
[Yue Ru]

894
00:35:01,450 --> 00:35:02,640
is very creative.

895
00:35:02,110 --> 00:35:03,290
[Ruhua Costume Company]

896
00:35:03,760 --> 00:35:05,530
Apparently, he's designed clothes

897
00:35:05,530 --> 00:35:06,230
for many stars

898
00:35:06,230 --> 00:35:07,340
and singers.

899
00:35:08,110 --> 00:35:09,090
I see that the things

900
00:35:09,090 --> 00:35:10,010
this company designs

901
00:35:10,010 --> 00:35:11,000
are all very trendy.

902
00:35:11,000 --> 00:35:12,230
It just so happens that this designer

903
00:35:12,230 --> 00:35:13,360
needs an assistant,

904
00:35:13,400 --> 00:35:13,900
so I recommended you

905
00:35:13,900 --> 00:35:14,630
to him.

906
00:35:16,090 --> 00:35:17,550
Recommended for me to work there?

907
00:35:17,550 --> 00:35:18,190
Yes.

908
00:35:19,840 --> 00:35:20,690
I was thinking

909
00:35:20,760 --> 00:35:21,880
you could give it a try

910
00:35:21,880 --> 00:35:22,780
if you need it.

911
00:35:23,050 --> 00:35:24,250
If it's not suitable,

912
00:35:24,590 --> 00:35:25,170
I won't force you.

913
00:35:25,170 --> 00:35:25,730
I need it.

914
00:35:27,030 --> 00:35:27,960
I really need it.

915
00:35:30,260 --> 00:35:30,800
Once you have

916
00:35:30,800 --> 00:35:31,880
a stable income,

917
00:35:31,940 --> 00:35:33,280
your family will be at ease.

918
00:35:33,280 --> 00:35:34,510
You don't need to worry

919
00:35:34,510 --> 00:35:36,130
about the tuition fees either.

920
00:35:36,130 --> 00:35:37,590
Just attend your classes,

921
00:35:38,190 --> 00:35:39,230
and don't let down

922
00:35:39,260 --> 00:35:41,120
Mr. Zheng's expectations of you.

923
00:35:41,510 --> 00:35:42,580
Right, Mr. Zheng?

924
00:35:44,170 --> 00:35:44,880
Mrs. Zheng,

925
00:35:45,280 --> 00:35:46,880
you're very understanding.

926
00:35:49,030 --> 00:35:50,290
Thank you, Mrs. Zheng.

927
00:35:52,260 --> 00:35:54,130
Why are you crying?

928
00:35:55,530 --> 00:35:56,210
From now on,

929
00:35:57,110 --> 00:35:58,730
work hard and sing well.

930
00:36:00,300 --> 00:36:01,360
Achieving success

931
00:36:02,010 --> 00:36:03,540
is the best repayment to us.

932
00:36:04,260 --> 00:36:04,710
I will.

933
00:36:08,710 --> 00:36:10,050
Mom. Mom.

934
00:36:10,900 --> 00:36:12,940
Dad sent a letter.

935
00:36:23,700 --> 00:36:26,260
[Guo Zongbao's Letter]

936
00:36:35,550 --> 00:36:35,900
Mom,

937
00:36:36,010 --> 00:36:37,130
why are you crying?

938
00:36:38,170 --> 00:36:39,500
What are you crying for?

939
00:36:50,670 --> 00:36:51,260
Mom.

940
00:36:51,940 --> 00:36:53,340
Dad said,

941
00:36:53,550 --> 00:36:54,280
next year,

942
00:36:54,630 --> 00:36:55,620
he'll take you

943
00:36:56,070 --> 00:36:57,630
to Beijing

944
00:36:57,980 --> 00:36:59,050
for surgery.

945
00:36:59,820 --> 00:37:03,380
He'll find the best experts
in the country.

946
00:37:05,590 --> 00:37:06,110
Mom,

947
00:37:07,400 --> 00:37:09,770
you'll be able to speak soon.

948
00:37:12,000 --> 00:37:13,710
You should be happy.

949
00:37:14,010 --> 00:37:17,530
I am happy. Happy.

950
00:37:23,530 --> 00:37:24,110
Mom.

951
00:37:24,900 --> 00:37:26,760
Dad also said

952
00:37:27,300 --> 00:37:28,900
he's making good money

953
00:37:29,480 --> 00:37:32,030
in Beijing.

954
00:37:32,960 --> 00:37:33,510
I...

955
00:37:33,570 --> 00:37:35,710
sometimes can't sleep at night.

956
00:37:36,610 --> 00:37:39,400
I think about how big Beijing is.

957
00:37:39,940 --> 00:37:41,920
Dad is so capable.

958
00:37:42,230 --> 00:37:44,160
He can act in Beijing.

959
00:37:44,780 --> 00:37:46,590
When I grow up,

960
00:37:47,300 --> 00:37:49,610
I'll join Dad

961
00:37:50,070 --> 00:37:52,000
to act in Beijing.

962
00:37:58,090 --> 00:38:00,050
Do you miss Dad?

963
00:38:11,090 --> 00:38:11,800
Mom.

964
00:38:12,610 --> 00:38:14,190
The other day at school,

965
00:38:14,960 --> 00:38:16,110
we had a show.

966
00:38:16,880 --> 00:38:19,510
I performed a skit.

967
00:38:20,510 --> 00:38:21,400
The principal

968
00:38:21,760 --> 00:38:23,050
said it was great.

969
00:38:24,840 --> 00:38:26,610
I told the principal

970
00:38:27,440 --> 00:38:30,150
it runs in the family.

971
00:38:52,260 --> 00:38:52,730
Thanks.

972
00:39:00,900 --> 00:39:03,360
[Ticket Office]

973
00:39:01,820 --> 00:39:02,150
Watch it.

974
00:39:02,150 --> 00:39:02,940
Sorry.

975
00:39:03,050 --> 00:39:04,250
I'm sorry, I'm sorry.

976
00:39:04,280 --> 00:39:05,090
No need. I'll do it myself.

977
00:39:05,090 --> 00:39:05,760
No problem.

978
00:39:07,770 --> 00:39:09,810
[Beijing to Nanjing]

979
00:39:08,010 --> 00:39:08,790
Seriously.

980
00:39:11,820 --> 00:39:13,180
Are your tickets fake?

981
00:39:15,880 --> 00:39:17,410
I've seen you here for days.

982
00:39:18,320 --> 00:39:19,250
I'm warning you.

983
00:39:19,590 --> 00:39:20,720
We're all scalpers.

984
00:39:21,030 --> 00:39:22,000
Don't meddle in my business.

985
00:39:22,000 --> 00:39:23,420
I'm buying for my company.

986
00:39:23,420 --> 00:39:23,820
You...

987
00:39:25,320 --> 00:39:26,820
So nosy. What bad luck.

988
00:39:27,010 --> 00:39:27,540
Get lost.

989
00:39:29,360 --> 00:39:30,590
Attention, everyone.

990
00:39:30,590 --> 00:39:31,860
Someone is selling fake tickets here!

991
00:39:31,570 --> 00:39:35,210
[Ticket Office]

992
00:39:35,240 --> 00:39:40,210
[Ticket Hall]

993
00:39:40,300 --> 00:39:41,940
[Enter the station with your ticket]
[Security Check]

994
00:39:42,190 --> 00:39:43,520
-Thank you.
-Thank you.

995
00:39:43,610 --> 00:39:44,470
Officer.

996
00:39:44,780 --> 00:39:45,790
I saw a man

997
00:39:45,980 --> 00:39:46,880
wearing a white shirt,

998
00:39:46,880 --> 00:39:48,030
carrying a black shoulder bag,

999
00:39:48,030 --> 00:39:49,730
and holding a bunch of tickets.

1000
00:39:49,730 --> 00:39:51,420
He was about this tall.

1001
00:39:51,840 --> 00:39:53,240
I suspect he's a scalper.

1002
00:39:53,650 --> 00:39:54,580
He went that way.

1003
00:39:54,820 --> 00:39:56,880
Okay. Thank you for the information.

1004
00:40:05,130 --> 00:40:05,930
Need tickets?

1005
00:40:07,070 --> 00:40:07,560
No.

1006
00:40:07,880 --> 00:40:08,500
Got them already, right?

1007
00:40:08,500 --> 00:40:08,860
Yes.

1008
00:40:08,900 --> 00:40:09,300
Okay.

1009
00:40:10,730 --> 00:40:11,490
Ladies.

1010
00:40:12,030 --> 00:40:13,440
Where are you going? Need tickets?

1011
00:40:13,440 --> 00:40:14,050
No, no, no.

1012
00:40:14,050 --> 00:40:15,510
We bought them ourselves.

1013
00:40:18,880 --> 00:40:19,330
Buddy.

1014
00:40:19,670 --> 00:40:20,800
Where are you going?

1015
00:40:20,860 --> 00:40:21,660
Need tickets?

1016
00:40:22,280 --> 00:40:23,280
Got them already?

1017
00:40:23,800 --> 00:40:24,190
Mom.

1018
00:40:24,880 --> 00:40:25,800
There's only one train

1019
00:40:25,800 --> 00:40:26,810
to Jiangxi.

1020
00:40:28,650 --> 00:40:29,170
Did you get tickets?

1021
00:40:29,170 --> 00:40:30,170
Let me check here.

1022
00:40:31,610 --> 00:40:33,270
There's nothing here either.

1023
00:40:33,440 --> 00:40:33,900
This...

1024
00:40:34,920 --> 00:40:35,340
Ma'am,

1025
00:40:36,210 --> 00:40:37,410
where are you headed?

1026
00:40:37,650 --> 00:40:38,400
Nanchang.

1027
00:40:38,630 --> 00:40:39,280
I have tickets.

1028
00:40:39,280 --> 00:40:40,630
I have tickets to everywhere.

1029
00:40:40,630 --> 00:40:42,030
-Do you want it?
-Really?

1030
00:40:42,190 --> 00:40:43,080
Let me see.

1031
00:40:43,580 --> 00:40:45,370
[Beijing to Nanjing]

1032
00:40:44,000 --> 00:40:45,400
Look. The ticket is fine.

1033
00:40:46,510 --> 00:40:47,770
All right. Give me two.

1034
00:40:48,010 --> 00:40:48,630
How much?

1035
00:40:48,800 --> 00:40:49,600
200 yuan each.

1036
00:40:50,230 --> 00:40:51,300
200?

1037
00:40:51,780 --> 00:40:52,380
At the ticket window,

1038
00:40:52,380 --> 00:40:53,940
it's only 80-something.

1039
00:40:54,670 --> 00:40:55,550
Keep it down.

1040
00:40:55,730 --> 00:40:56,340
If you can't afford it,

1041
00:40:56,340 --> 00:40:57,280
go to the window.

1042
00:40:58,000 --> 00:40:59,500
No, look.

1043
00:40:59,670 --> 00:41:01,230
My father-in-law is sick.

1044
00:41:01,270 --> 00:41:02,770
I have to go back today.

1045
00:41:02,920 --> 00:41:03,780
They said at the window

1046
00:41:03,780 --> 00:41:05,210
that there are no tickets left.

1047
00:41:05,210 --> 00:41:06,190
People come here to buy tickets

1048
00:41:06,190 --> 00:41:07,860
for urgent matters.

1049
00:41:07,900 --> 00:41:09,030
I can't sell to you without the money.

1050
00:41:09,030 --> 00:41:09,760
No, no, sir.

1051
00:41:09,760 --> 00:41:10,230
No, no.

1052
00:41:10,320 --> 00:41:10,920
Let's talk this over.

1053
00:41:10,920 --> 00:41:11,980
What are you doing?

1054
00:41:12,130 --> 00:41:13,300
Aren't these tickets

1055
00:41:13,300 --> 00:41:14,700
bought for your company?

1056
00:41:15,420 --> 00:41:16,350
You bought them?

1057
00:41:16,460 --> 00:41:17,000
Come on, give me the tickets.

1058
00:41:17,000 --> 00:41:18,510
No, explain it clearly first.

1059
00:41:18,510 --> 00:41:19,310
Young man,

1060
00:41:19,480 --> 00:41:20,030
do you have

1061
00:41:20,030 --> 00:41:21,110
tickets to Nanchang?

1062
00:41:21,110 --> 00:41:21,780
No.

1063
00:41:21,780 --> 00:41:22,300
Yes,

1064
00:41:22,340 --> 00:41:23,780
I have tickets to Nanchang.

1065
00:41:23,780 --> 00:41:24,320
Great.

1066
00:41:24,400 --> 00:41:25,650
Please sell me two.

1067
00:41:26,280 --> 00:41:28,030
My father-in-law is sick.

1068
00:41:28,320 --> 00:41:29,880
They said there are no tickets left
at the counter.

1069
00:41:29,880 --> 00:41:30,960
We're not selling anything. We can't.

1070
00:41:30,960 --> 00:41:31,840
These are for our company.

1071
00:41:31,840 --> 00:41:32,980
How much did he say

1072
00:41:32,980 --> 00:41:34,070
a ticket costs?

1073
00:41:35,230 --> 00:41:35,760
200.

1074
00:41:38,840 --> 00:41:39,730
How many do you need?

1075
00:41:39,730 --> 00:41:41,260
I'll sell them to you at face value.

1076
00:41:41,260 --> 00:41:42,050
I need two.

1077
00:41:46,570 --> 00:41:47,770
Mom, take the ticket.

1078
00:41:48,710 --> 00:41:49,410
Young man,

1079
00:41:49,550 --> 00:41:51,440
I won't let you do this for nothing.

1080
00:41:51,440 --> 00:41:52,000
180.

1081
00:41:52,630 --> 00:41:53,840
No need. 170 is fine.

1082
00:41:54,500 --> 00:41:55,390
Thank you.

1083
00:41:55,590 --> 00:41:56,560
Mom, let's go.

1084
00:41:56,690 --> 00:41:57,280
Hurry up and go.

1085
00:41:57,280 --> 00:41:58,500
You're such a rip-off!

1086
00:41:58,500 --> 00:41:59,420
Hurry. Let's go, Mom.

1087
00:41:59,420 --> 00:42:00,880
We're running out of time.

1088
00:42:03,480 --> 00:42:04,120
What?

1089
00:42:05,260 --> 00:42:06,860
Done being a Good Samaritan?

1090
00:42:07,570 --> 00:42:08,990
Are you out of your mind?

1091
00:42:09,300 --> 00:42:10,480
I brought you here to make money.

1092
00:42:10,480 --> 00:42:11,570
Why are you fighting me on this?

1093
00:42:11,570 --> 00:42:13,280
Does this have anything to do with money?

1094
00:42:13,280 --> 00:42:14,280
Why did you lie to me?

1095
00:42:14,280 --> 00:42:14,860
Didn't you say

1096
00:42:14,860 --> 00:42:16,230
they were tickets for the company?

1097
00:42:16,230 --> 00:42:17,630
This is called scalping.

1098
00:42:17,860 --> 00:42:19,460
Fine, fine. You're the boss.

1099
00:42:19,630 --> 00:42:20,690
Can we keep it down?

1100
00:42:21,010 --> 00:42:21,660
I give up.

1101
00:42:22,210 --> 00:42:22,920
Give me the tickets.

1102
00:42:22,920 --> 00:42:23,280
No.

1103
00:42:23,880 --> 00:42:24,530
I paid for them.

1104
00:42:24,530 --> 00:42:26,130
Why won't you give them to me?

1105
00:42:26,760 --> 00:42:27,800
Then I'll give you the money.

1106
00:42:27,800 --> 00:42:28,840
I don't want money. I want the tickets.

1107
00:42:28,840 --> 00:42:29,860
-Come on, give me the tickets.
-Stop pulling.

1108
00:42:29,860 --> 00:42:30,780
I'm going to scream.

1109
00:42:30,780 --> 00:42:31,640
I'm screaming.

1110
00:42:33,200 --> 00:42:34,260
Okay, okay. Fine.

1111
00:42:34,510 --> 00:42:36,240
Give me the money. Hand it over.

1112
00:42:37,460 --> 00:42:37,980
I don't get it.

1113
00:42:37,980 --> 00:42:39,240
What are you thinking?

1114
00:42:39,300 --> 00:42:40,170
You make so little money,

1115
00:42:40,170 --> 00:42:41,340
and it hasn't even warmed your pocket.

1116
00:42:41,340 --> 00:42:42,340
What's the point?

1117
00:42:42,920 --> 00:42:44,420
No wonder you're an artist.

1118
00:42:44,420 --> 00:42:45,780
What's wrong with doing art?

1119
00:42:45,780 --> 00:42:47,340
I'd rather starve to death
than take your money!

1120
00:42:47,340 --> 00:42:48,800
Shut your mouth. Give me the money.

1121
00:42:48,800 --> 00:42:50,010
Don't move, both of you.

1122
00:42:50,010 --> 00:42:51,570
Please cooperate with our investigation.

1123
00:42:51,570 --> 00:42:52,550
He... He is reselling illegally.

1124
00:42:52,550 --> 00:42:53,220
Quiet!

1125
00:42:53,460 --> 00:42:54,940
We'll know once the investigation is done.
